    howToGetThere: "Drive from Pokhara to Beni (2\u20133 hours, 70 km) then by jeep or bus along the Kali Gandaki road to Tatopani (2\u20133 more hours, 60 km). Alternatively, reach Tatopani on foot via the Annapurna Circuit from Marpha (descending south) or from Ghorepani (descending north). The road is now accessible by jeep year-round in normal conditions.",
