    howToGetThere: "Bhaktapur is 13 km east of Kathmandu. Take a local bus or taxi to Bhaktapur Durbar Square, then walk south through the narrow lanes past Kedarnath temple for about 5\u201310 minutes to reach Pottery Square (Bolachha Tole). Taxis from Thamel cost approximately NPR 500\u2013700.",
