    howToGetThere: "Changu Narayan is 12 km east of Kathmandu and 5 km north of Bhaktapur. Take a taxi from Kathmandu (NPR 800\u20131,000, 45 minutes) or a bus to Bhaktapur and then a local microbus or taxi up to Changunarayan village. A popular approach is the 12\u201315 km hike from Nagarkot along the ridge trail through Tamang villages.",
